con:config.con:query: SELECT M.MARKETTYPE,M.INITIATORBANKID,M.CUSTOMERID,TRANSACTIONSID,debit_booking_ID,M.AGREEMENTID,PI.PAYMENTINFOID,HT.DEBETACCOUNTNO, PAYMENTSTATUS FROM HST_MESSAGE M INNER JOIN HST_PAYMENTINFO PI ON MESSAGEID = FK_MESSAGEID INNER JOIN HST_TRANSACTIONS HT ON PAYMENTINFOID = FK_PAYMENTINFOID WHERE M.INITIATORBANKID='4201' and paymentstatus='COMP' and HT.debit_booking_ID!='NULL' and length(debit_booking_ID)!=11 ORDER BY TRANSACTIONSID DESC fetch first 3rows only
